############################################################
# casa
countchannel.py (countchannel_2110.py):
Count the number of channels used in making moment 0 map.
1) The threshold is 2*rms

makemask_mod.py (makemask.py):
Make the mask of different regions of the galaxy based on the
morphology. 

ratio_1213.py:
Make the ratio map of 12CO/13CO. 

ratio_2110_5rms.py (ratio_2110_mask.py):
Make the ratio map of 12CO2-1/1-0 based on rms threshold or the mask
drawn by hand. 

anomaly_kin.py:
Make the mask of the region with anomaly velocity. 

############################################################
# python

opDepth.py: 
Calculate the optcial depth of 12CO and 13CO based on the
Jimenez_Donaire. 2017. 

color_ratio.py:
Try different colors for the poster ratio map. 

measure_1213/
NGC5257_measure_mod_error.py
(NGC5257_measure_mod.py,NGC5257_measure_mod_1213.py):
Measure the ratio of the 12CO/13CO in different regions.

measure_2110/
NGC5257_measure_2110_mod_error.py:
(NGC5257_measure_2110.py)
Measure the ratio of the 12CO2-1/1-0 in different regions. 

